com.hp.jipp.encoding

Interface AttributeGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PrettyPrintable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MutableAttributeGroup

    public AttributeGroup
extends PrettyPrintable

    A tagged list of attributes. Only one attribute of a given type may appear in the group, although each attribute may contain 0 or more values.
